    <textblock>
      Post-marketing surveillance registry of the CardioRoot graft.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study objective is to monitor the performance and safety of CardioRoot vascular grafts
      implanted in a thoracic position. Patient survival rates will be monitored as well as
      immediate and long-term complications.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
