  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients requiring a CardioRoot graft as per the CardioRoot IFU

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with contra-indications per CardioRoot IFU

          -  patients requiring consecutive aortic surgery

          -  patients with coronary artery disease

